Sneak away for once in a lifetime sunset photos on your wedding day.
The power of storytelling in a single frame.

I grew up in photography shooting film. I would have to run two bodies, one w/color film, one w/black & white film. I had to decide which camera to shoot in the moment. I learned to see in black & white. The three top things I look for in a stunning black & white image…  1. Beautiful directional available light.  2. Emotion. 
3. Movement. 

When you can capture all three in a single frame it can be very rewarding as an artist.
